<div data-controller="portal" class="mx-auto">
  <div class="pb-6 flex justify-between items-center">
    <h1 class="text-gray-500 text-3xl tracking-tighter items-center px-1 pt-1 font-bold">Tournament Management</h1>
      <div class="flex gap-2 items-center pb-1 flow-root py-1">
        <button id="dropdownDefaultButton" data-dropdown-toggle="dropdown" class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-full text-md px-5 py-1 text-center inline-flex items-center dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800" type="button">Create Tournament <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 ms-3" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m1 1 4 4 4-4"/>
        </svg>
        </button>

        <!-- Dropdown menu -->
        <div id="dropdown" class="z-10 hidden bg-gray-100 divide-y divide-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow w-44 dark:bg-gray-700">
          <ul class="py-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200" aria-labelledby="dropdownDefaultButton">
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="group flex block px-4 py-2 hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:text-white rounded-full"
                data-action="portal#newTournamentTeamClick">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
                </svg>&nbsp;&nbsp;Team Based
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="group flex block px-4 py-2 hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:text-white rounded-full"
                data-action="portal#newTournamentPlayerClick">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
                </svg>&nbsp;&nbsp;Player Based</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>    
    <%# link_to 'New Player', new_user_path, class: "inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-transparent text-xs font-medium rounded text-indigo-700 bg-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-indigo-500" %>
  </div>

  <div id="tournaments" class="min-w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="-my-2 overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
        <div class="py-2 align-middle inline-block min-w-full sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <% if @tournaments.count == 0 %>
            <div class="py-4 text-center text-md font-medium tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-600 md:text-md lg:text-md">
              Such nothingness :( <br><br>Create a tournament and start having some fun!
            </div>
            <div class="justify-center flex">
              
              <div class="w-1/3 rounded-lg border-dashed p-4 border-2 border-gray-500 italic text-sm font-medium md:text-md lg:text-md">
                <div class="py-4 text-sm text-center font-medium leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-md lg:text-md">
                  <span class="text-gray-500">Create players first by <%= link_to "clicking here", players_path, class: "text-blue-500" %>.</span>
                </div>       
                <div class="text-gray-500 text-justify">           
                  Are you aware of the Timer functionality? When you create a Tournament, you can choose a "Match" and "Break" time.
                  The Match time is how long your Matches will run for. The Break time is the pre-start time for each Match.
                  When you're on the Tournament viewing page, on the top left you can click to reveal a side menu. There is a toggle
                  to hide and show the Timer top section of the page.
                  
                  Besides Timer controls, you have the ability to update scoring as well from the side menu.<br><br>
                </div>
              

              </div>
                
            </div>

         
          <% else %>     
            <div class="shadow overflow-hidden border-b border-gray-200 sm:rounded-lg">   
              <%= render "tournaments/tournaments_table" %> 
            </div>
          <% end %>    
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
